title: American_Top_10_Christmas_At_The_Movies
description:
"From Snowflake, Arizona, to Snowbird, Utah, and from Peace, Alaska, to Star, Mississippi, we're celebrating the holiday season on American Top 10."


This is a rebroadcast of a countdown show hosted by Casey Kasem subsequent to AT40. The show was called American Top 10. I have no idea of the original air date.

Happy Holidays!
